name: Experiment Or Die #33
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of photos and personal assets. I'm on day 33 of creating these collages so haven't been around for very long. But I have been collecting and customizing designer toys for about 15 years and this piece is a tribute to just a few of my customs mixed in with some iconic stuff from my collection. IG and Twitter: Nikejerk
